ernate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266353/nintendo-alarmo-sound-clock</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name><name>克里斯·韦尔奇</name><name>杰·彼得斯</name><name>安德鲁·韦伯斯特</name><name>理查德·劳勒</name><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T15:39:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T15:39:00-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 Prime Day 第二天您可以买到的最优惠商品</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Prime Day 期间提供的各种产品的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/tm2JnOqRCfx0OYc9chLKchgFuso=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73638984/247273_Prime_Big_Deals_Days_2024_CV irginia_POST_EVENT_ROUNDUP.5.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;无论您是想要一副耳机、智能家居升级、充电器还是其他东西，仍然有时间节省各种技术完全不同。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024 &quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T15:20:47-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T15:20:47-04:00</updated><title>苹果 Vision Pro 负责人 Dan Riccio 即将退休</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;2021 年 Dan Riccio 的个人资料图片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/OOj5bzBXA3OLE-J8x6WJhZtZr7M=/0x28:1960x1335/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642902/Apple_dan_riccio_begins_a_new_chapter_at_apple_01252020_big.jpg.large_2x.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;照片：Apple&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;cj6klG&quot;>;Dan Riccio，苹果资深员工前负责硬件的高管将于本月从公司退休，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-09/apple-s-dan-riccio-key-高管在工作和厨师时代退休>;&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;报道&lt;/a>;。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;laj9u5&quot;>;Riccio 已在 Apple 工作 26 年。在 2012 年成为硬件工程高级副总裁之前，他 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2012/6/28/3124498/apple-svp-of-hardware-engineering-bob-mansfield-retiring&quot; >;领导公司的 iPad 部门&lt;/a>;。正如彭博社指出的那样，作为公司的硬件主管，他负责监督公司一些最成功的产品，包括 AirPods 和大型 iPhone。他还领导了 Apple Car 等项目，但这些项目从未成为现实&lt;/a>;，以及 Vision Pro，后者一直在努力站稳脚跟。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VuDE5r&quot;>;他被替换为硬件工程高级副总裁&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/1/25/22249393/apple-senior-vice-president -hardware-engineering-dan-riccio-john-ternus-new&quot;>;约翰·特努斯于 2021 年&lt;/a>;。当时，据说他正在接管一个未具体说明的“新项目”，最终&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2021/2/8/22272555/apple-dan-riccio-ar- vr-development&quot;>;结果是&lt;/a>;...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266321/apple-dan -riccio-retiring&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266321/apple-dan-riccio-retiring" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266321/apple-dan-riccio-retiring</id><author><name>韦斯·戴维斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T15:15:12-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T15:15:12-04:00</updated><title>仔细看看任天堂可爱的闹钟</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;任天堂 Alarmo 闹钟的照片。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/dc70nlQ5xP5uLsxdEH92Al14ggQ=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642892/DSC_0974.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;这款昂贵的床头时钟可以感应您的动作，并用任天堂喜爱的角色叫醒您。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24266272/nintendo- Alarmo-sound-clock-hands-on&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24266272/nintendo-alarmo-sound-clock-hands-on" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24266272/nintendo-alarmo-sound-clock-hands-on</id><author><name>克里斯·