on.com/dp/B08D9N7RJ4 ?tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;飞利浦 Hue RGB 智能灯泡&lt;/a>;，以及 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CFXQMZJT? tag=theverge02-20&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Anker 的 MagGo 三合一充电座&lt;/a>;。不过，这些 Prime Day 优惠只能保证再持续一天，因为促销活动预计只持续到今天 10 月 9 日......&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024</id><author><name>昆汀·肯内默</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T14:47:34-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T14:47:34-04:00</updated><title> X 将向其高级用户付费以使其相互交流</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;X 徽标的矢量拼贴画。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/BZXD7MB2u8EmPOWnaIKjNe-L1hA=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642824/STK160_X_TWITTER_2__A.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;pbr5q1&quot;>;X 正在对创作者从平台赚钱的方式做出重大改变。自去年以来，X &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2023/7/28/23811535/x-twitter-ads-revenue-sharing-program-creators&quot;>;与创作者分享广告收入&lt; /a>; 基于有多少经过验证的用户在回复其帖子时看到广告。但该公司&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/X/status/1844066291625361812&quot;>;今天宣布&lt;/a>;，创作者将根据“高级用户对您内容的参与度”来获得报酬。&lt; /p>; &lt;p id=&quot;XgtNUs&quot;>;换句话说：订阅 X Premium 并与其他 Premium 订阅者的内容互动的人越多，他们赚的钱就越多。理论上。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Jf5lYZ&quot;>;如果我不得不猜测的话，真正发生的情况是高级用户在回复中出现的次数甚至会比现在更多。订阅 X Premium 的人&lt;em>;已经&lt;/em>;在推文回复中获得优先权，并且优先级取决于哪个 X Premium...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266258/x-pay-premium-users-engage-with-each-other&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266258/x-pay-premium-users-engage-with-each-other" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266258/x-pay-premium-users-engage-with-each-other</id><author><name>杰·彼得斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T14:38:44-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T14:38:44-04:00</updated><title>我们为亚马逊 Prime Day 找到的最佳笔记本电脑优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Asus Zenbook Duo 处于双屏模式。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/p48wWJ8xKtt46pJj947iWtVOhSw=/0x0:2700x1800/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73642810/246951_Asus_Zenbook_Duo_ABenedet to_0213.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;想象一下，获得这一切并在此过程中节省近 300 美元。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Antonio G. Di Benedetto / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;M4y5kP&quot;>;亚马逊并不以提供最优惠的笔记本电脑而闻名，但它的&lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;>;正在进行的 Prime Big Deal Days 销售活动&lt;/a>;有一些实实在在的折扣 —如果考虑到&lt;a href=&quot;https://howl.me/cngroop5STO&quot;>;百思买的“48小时闪购”&lt;/a>;反计划，还有更多。如果您正在市场上购买新的 MacBook、Windows 生产力机器（包括新的 Copilot Plus PC），甚至是游戏笔记本电脑，我们会为您提供一些有价值的选择。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id= &quot;bnxbfQ&quot;>;虽然像百思买这样的专业电子零售商可能因日常笔记本电脑折扣而闻名，但亚马逊也有其公平的份额。如果您购买 MacBook，尤其如此，其中一些 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/8/24265354/apple-macbook-air-13-15-m3 -processor-october-prime-day-deal-sale&quot;>;亚马逊目前拥有迄今为止的最低价格&lt;/a>;。当然，您不会获得广泛的选择...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303 /amazon-prime-day-best-buy-sale-laptop-macbook-windows-gaming-deal&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303/amazon-prime-day-best-buy-sale-laptop-macbook-windows-gaming-deal" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/good-deals/2024/10/9/24262303/ama